{"tid":1784004,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"港台新聞可能係香港最好","createTime":"2019-12-15T10:32:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-31T13:52:37.000Z","uid":314617,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1d8dbe48d2ea4f163b20e0f60a3c16fd5047cce6","tid":1784004,"uid":314617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T10:32:43.000Z","msg":"據小弟所知，<br />\n港台新聞被指係「好過無綫新聞嘅中立媒體」，<br />\n甚至有唔少戶外廣告公司都利用之，<br />\n作為「新聞列」。<br />\n<br />\n相比電視，<br />\n港台新聞最成功嘅地方在於報道全面<br />\n而不至於徧坦於某一方<br />\n（ex. 東方日報&mdash;徧建制；蘋果日報&mdash;徧泛民），<br />\n所以可以話係全香港最好，<br />\n尤其係喺報道本地新聞嗰陣，<br />\n呢個優勢尤其明顯。<br />\n<br />\n歡迎討論。"},{"pid":"b412a67d28a91a0c1d7a28d041e153d7014f6354","tid":1784004,"uid":202524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T10:34:47.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 借個位黎<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">德國戰線要人</span></span><br />\n<br />\n冇時間啦25號截止，極度要人幫手!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1782422\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1782422</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c82c3889c92444fc13dc8be4fdc85a7c39d395c9","tid":1784004,"uid":66882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T10:34:52.000Z","msg":"就算唔計立場 港台都係最屈機"},{"pid":"e2a4384430da3024fab5ef0add5c410927360bb1","tid":1784004,"uid":313203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T10:37:40.000Z","msg":"要數港台唔不是就係播狗訊，除此外冇嘢唔好"},{"pid":"7d90afbff2953bb2a390e155fd6ca8b8c3abbd81","tid":1784004,"uid":175623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T10:41:40.000Z","msg":"［行動post] 1224 全城出街慶聖誕<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1782999\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1782999</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5c61d5e0315432cc7a0a7e7fc88c46b0dec7b774","tid":1784004,"uid":344564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T18:13:46.000Z","msg":"Now新聞同有線都係好好既傳媒機構"},{"pid":"bb3be6fa5684af25946bd790a192cebeeb7da3e0","tid":1784004,"uid":31